Title: Backup: Fix adding / editing backup jobs with manual schedule
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1615368095
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p1

When adding or editing backup jobs with a "manual schedule" configuration this
lead to an exception "TypeError (argument of type 'NoneType' is not iterable)"
in previous 2.0.0 releases.
